WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.750
Did you know Franklin County Public Library has Virginia State Park Discovery Backpacks and Parking passes

2
00:00:05.751 --> 00:00:07.000
available for check out?

3
00:00:07.001 --> 00:00:08.750
In this one kit, you get everything you need 

4
00:00:08.751 --> 00:00:12.000
for a fun day exploring nature at your local state parks.

5
00:00:12.001 --> 00:00:13.500
In addition to a parking pass,

6
00:00:13.501 --> 00:00:16.500
the kit includes nature guides full of detailed, color images

7
00:00:16.501 --> 00:00:19.000
to help guide you through your surroundings

8
00:00:19.001 --> 00:00:22.000
and activity sheets and information to help guide your adventures.

9
00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.500
Your backpack will also contain an observation container

10
00:00:25.501 --> 00:00:34.000
magnifying glass, dip net, compass, binoculars, ruler, and forceps

11
00:00:34.001 --> 00:00:35.500
to help you make the most out of your day!

12
00:00:35.501 --> 00:00:39.000
Backpacks are available for checkout at the Rocky Mount children's desk

13
00:00:39.001 --> 00:00:40.900
and the Westlake circulation desk

14
00:00:40.901 --> 00:00:43.000
and have a two week check out period.

15
00:00:43.001 --> 00:00:47.750
This backpack is the perfect addition to your summer adventures in our beautiful state parks

16
00:00:47.751 --> 00:00:50.000
Be sure to come check yours out soon!